des:
Quantum computers could one day provide breakthroughs in many disciplines, including materials and drug discovery, and artificial intelligence. 
Ask Alexa for an interesting list of facts to understand what Quantum Computing is. 
When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next fact. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
